data.name: dodoSetupBtn.ToolTip
data.value:
Enable the "Dodo Helper" and monitor your online connection. If your island is disconnected due to whatever reason, it will try to restore the Dodo code automatically.
Noted that you will need to give the player control to the virtual controller. You cannot have other controller connected at the same time. Some virtual controller buttons are provided if you need to use it real quick.
